title: Jeep Liberty Limited Urban Terrain Stroller Baby Mom Safety Travel Kent
text: Jeep Liberty Limited Urban Terrain Stroller Baby mom Safety Travel (Kent) Stroller in Seattle, WA Chicco, Graco, Jeep, Peg Perego Last Update: Originally Posted On: SpreadMyAd Additional Comments: Selling my stroller that have no use of anymore. It is in mint condition with no tears, rips or holes. Nice and clean. Asking $120 obo Here's the details about: Pattern/color: Black/green/white Includes front and parent tray Customize the Liberty to be your own travel system using favorite brands such as Chicco, Graco, and Peg Perego infant car seats iBaby Sound System which lets you hook up your iPod or mp3 player for Music on the Move With a simple click you can change the front wheel from swivel to locked Rugged 12-inch inflatable tires grip all types of terrain and provide a smooth ride Easy swivel front wheel locks for uneven surfaces and turns easily in tight spaces JPMA certified Weight/height limit: 50 lbs Stroller weight: 30 lbs Materials: Steel/plastic/polyester fabric Dimensions folded: 34.75 ins high x 26ins wide x 17.5ins deep
